# JAQL Project

Modular C++23 quantitative finance library. All generated code must conform to `docs/`.

## Module Layers (strict one-way dependencies)

```
Foundation:  infra → core → math
Domain:      instruments, market, curves
Analytics:   pricing, simulation, risk, portfolio
```

See [docs/architecture/module-dependencies.md](docs/architecture/module-dependencies.md).

## Layout

- Headers: `include/jaql/<module>/`
- Sources: `src/<module>/`
- Unit tests: `tests/unit/<module>/`

## Build & Test

```bash
./scripts/bootstrap.sh
cmake --build --preset gcc-debug
./scripts/test.sh
./scripts/format.sh --check
./scripts/lint.sh
```

Default preset: `gcc-debug`. CI presets: `ci-gcc-debug`, `ci-clang-debug`, etc.

